Value: NameWithoutSpaces2, Description: Name With Spaces2
```

Note that this assumes your enum values have a corresponding `FieldInfo` with the same name. If you're using an anonymous enum or something similar, this might not work.

Also note that we're caching the results of reflection operations to avoid repeated calls and improve performance. This is generally good practice when working with reflection in .NET.

